-- Palestinian Prime Minister Fayyad Hospitalized With Infection
-- B y   F a d w a   H o d a l i
-- 2013-04-01T20:48:59Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-04-01/palestinian-prime-minister-fayyad-hospitalized-with-infection.html
Palestinian Prime Minister Salam Fayyad was hospitalized with a stomach infection and will be
kept overnight for observation at Ramallah Medical Center in the
 West Bank , Health Minister Hani Abdeen said.  Aside from the stomach ailment, Fayyad is in good health,
Abdeen said today by phone. The prime minister suffered a heart
attack in 2011 while visiting the U.S,  Fayyad has been prime minister since 2007.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Fadwa Hodali in Jerusalem at 
 fhodali@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
